\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>Maggie<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3>(In disbelief, continuing to put the puzzle pieces together after the fact.):<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs26\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I can\u8217\'92t believe this is happening. Is this why the two of you have been acting so strange the last couple of weeks?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>Laura<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3>(Sincerely caring):<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs26\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We just want to help you.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>Maggie<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3>(Defensive):<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs26\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I told you before, Laura, I\u8217\'92m not a charity case.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>Laura<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3>(Pleading, caring):<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs26\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I didn\u8217\'92t say you were. But I see nothing wrong in accepting help from the people who love you. You work so hard and never catch a break. You deserve this! Please accept the scholarship,\u8221\'94 }
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>Maggie<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3>(}{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 Distressed, Upset,buried her face in her hands, repeating an earlier sentiment}{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 ):<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs26\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I can\u8217\'92t believe this is happening. You two had no right to go behind my back and set this whole thing up.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>Evan<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3>(Caring and helpful tone intended):<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs26\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Don\u8217\'92t let your pride sabotage your success, Maggie.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>Maggie<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3>(Misinterpreting Evan's tone as condescending and psychoanalyzing.):<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs26\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Evan, please don\u8217\'92t psychoanalyze me. We are not talking about $50 here or even $500. This is $15,000!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>Laura<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3>(}{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 Laura saw an opportunity to make a point.}{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 ):<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That may be a lot of money to me and you, but Evan makes that much in just a week or two. He gets that whether he works or not.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>Evan<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3>(In sync, with Laura. Jumps in to expound upon her point):<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs26\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That\u8217\'92s true. That money was just sitting in my bank doing no one any good.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>Maggie<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3>(Maggie was shocked to say the least. She had no idea Evan made that much money.):<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs26\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You really make that much?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0 Evan nodded yes.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>Laura<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3>(Expounding on her and Evan's current line of persuasion.):<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs26\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93And he doesn\u8217\'92t have any mortgage or car payments. His monthly expenses are less than ours. So, there\u8217\'92s no reason for you not to accept this gift.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs26\b1\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::2>Maggie<!$Scr_Cs::2>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3>(Sarcastically, still frustrated, but her resolve is finally beginning to show cracks.):<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs26\b0\i0 "What are you, his accountant?\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94 }{\f3\fs26\b0\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::3>\{then let out a sound that was a combination of a sigh and a grunt.)<!$Scr_Cs::3>}
